he's embedding instructions
into a disorientating syntax.

00:07:45.007 --> 00:07:45.590 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes.

00:07:45.590 --> 00:07:46.881 align:middle line:90%
>>KRAMER: And kind of language.

