00:08:18.640 --> 00:08:20.420 align:middle line:84%
And you realize
that that is what's

00:08:20.420 --> 00:08:22.685 align:middle line:84%
going on with all
the media and all

00:08:22.685 --> 00:08:25.200 align:middle line:90%
the educational institutions.

